Class User

  • java.lang.Object
    • photoAlbum.model.User
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class User
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    User class that contains username and password, all of user's albums, and lists of photos in the user's albums that contain certain tags.
